---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/layout/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/layout/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="Learn about The Copilot Stack - your comprehensive resource for Microsoft Copilot extensibility."
>
  <Header />
  <main class="flex-grow container mx-auto px-4 py-8">
    <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto prose prose-invert">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold text-terminal-green mb-6 terminal-prompt">
        About The Copilot Stack
      </h1>

      <div class="text-terminal-white space-y-6">
        <p class="text-xl">
          Welcome to <strong class="text-terminal-green">The Copilot Stack</strong> - your comprehensive resource for Microsoft Copilot extensibility.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-terminal-green mt-8 mb-4 terminal-prompt">
          Our Mission
        </h2>
        <p>
          We aim to empower developers and organizations to build powerful extensions for Microsoft Copilot.
          Through in-depth technical content, video tutorials, and podcast episodes, we share practical
          knowledge, best practices, and real-world examples of Copilot extensibility.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-terminal-green mt-8 mb-4 terminal-prompt">
          What We Offer
        </h2>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-2 text-terminal-white">
          <li>
            <strong class="text-terminal-green">Technical Blog Posts:</strong> Detailed articles covering
            Copilot extensibility topics, development patterns, and implementation guides.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong class="text-terminal-green">Video Tutorials:</strong> Visual walkthroughs of building
            Copilot extensions, available on YouTube.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong class="text-terminal-green">Podcast Episodes:</strong> Deep dives into Copilot extensibility
            topics, available on Spotify and Apple Music.
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-terminal-green mt-8 mb-4 terminal-prompt">
          Topics We Cover
        </h2>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-2 text-terminal-white">
          <li>Microsoft Copilot API and SDK usage</li>
          <li>Building custom plugins and extensions</li>
          <li>Integration patterns and best practices</li>
          <li>Authentication and security considerations</li>
          <li>Performance optimization techniques</li>
          <li>Real-world case studies and examples</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-terminal-green mt-8 mb-4 terminal-prompt">
          About the Author
        </h2>
        <p>
          <strong class="text-terminal-green">Sébastien Levert</strong> is a passionate developer advocate
          and Microsoft Copilot enthusiast. With years of experience in building enterprise solutions and
          developer tools, Sébastien shares practical insights and hands-on guidance for developers looking
          to extend Microsoft Copilot's capabilities.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-terminal-green mt-8 mb-4 terminal-prompt">
          Get Involved
        </h2>
        <p>
          The Copilot Stack is an open-source project. We welcome contributions, feedback, and suggestions
          from the community. Whether you want to suggest topics, report issues, or contribute content,
          we'd love to hear from you.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 mt-8">
          <a href="https://github.com/sebastienlevert/the-copilot-stack" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn">
            GitHub Repository
          </a>
          <a href="https://twitter.com/sebastienlevert" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn bg-terminal-gray border border-terminal-greenDim text-terminal-green hover:bg-terminal-greenDim hover:text-terminal-black">
            Follow on Twitter/X
          </a>
          <a href="https://youtube.com/@sebastienlevert" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn bg-terminal-gray border border-terminal-greenDim text-terminal-green hover:bg-terminal-greenDim hover:text-terminal-black">
            YouTube Channel
          </a>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-terminal-green mt-8 mb-4 terminal-prompt">
          Technology Stack
        </h2>
        <p>
          This website is built with modern web technologies for optimal performance and developer experience:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-2 text-terminal-white">
          <li><strong class="text-terminal-green">Astro:</strong> Static site generator for content-heavy sites</li>
          <li><strong class="text-terminal-green">TypeScript:</strong> Type-safe development</li>
          <li><strong class="text-terminal-green">Tailwind CSS:</strong> Utility-first styling</li>
          <li><strong class="text-terminal-green">MDX:</strong> Markdown with component support</li>
          <li><strong class="text-terminal-green">GitHub Pages:</strong> Fast and reliable hosting</li>
          <li><strong class="text-terminal-green">Pagefind:</strong> Client-side search</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="mt-12 p-6 bg-terminal-gray border border-terminal-greenDim rounded-lg">
          <p class="text-center text-terminal-greenDim">
            Want to stay updated? Subscribe to our <a href="/rss.xml" class="text-terminal-green hover:underline">RSS feed</a>
            or follow us on social media for the latest posts and episodes.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
